# Task 035 Summary - Sweep Signature Probe

## Headline

Task 035 adds the Layer 1 `sweep_signature_probe` primitive. It composes `typed_finite_difference` and `typed_log_log_slope` into a typed `SweepSignatureValue` and emits seven `SweepSignatureStatus` strata for clean sweeps, cancellation dominance, high drop rate, degenerate input, insufficient data, all-nonfinite cells, and all-domain-refused cells.

